{"type":null,"faqId":8973,"title":"荣耀3X（G750-T00）什么是GPS加速和AGPS？和AGPS有何差异？","answer":"<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">如果开启数据业务，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">加速打开后，会打开</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">AGPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">和自动下载</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">EPO</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">离线辅助</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">能够提高</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">定位速度。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">加速是一种统称。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">AGPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">是辅助全球卫星定位系统（英语：</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">Assisted Global Positioning System</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，简称：</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">AGPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">）的简称，是一种</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">的运行方式。它可以利用手机基地站的资讯，配合传统</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">卫星，让定位的速度更快。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">EPO</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">是联发科创新出的一项基于离线服务器的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">辅助定位技术。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">支持</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">卫星轨道预测，这些数据可以大幅缩短</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Arial','sans-serif';\">GPS</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">卫星首次定位时间，提升用户体验</span>","faqTypeId":142,"faqType":"位置服务与导航","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9559","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Location-Navigation","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1396085716000,"seriesProductName":"G750-T00","visitedTimes":351,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":7,"times":7,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"GPS","avgScore":1.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}